	<h2 class="item-title" itemprop="headline">
			Surf Lessons In Taghazout - Learn to Surf with the Best!		</h2>








<hr />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Argana Surf School is based at the centre of MA surfing; Taghazout in Cornwall and we've been teaching people to surf for <strong>over 18 years.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">As well as being one of the longest running MA Surf Schools we are <strong>the only Surf School in Newquay</strong> to boast <strong>not one, but two Ex-Professional Surfers</strong> on their Full Time Coaching Team: <strong>&nbsp;Head Coach <a href="about-us/the-team/96-head-coach-mike-young.html" target="_blank">Mike Young</a></strong>&nbsp; &amp; <strong>Senior Coach <a href="about-us/the-team/171-reubin-pearce-surf-coach.html" target="_blank">Reubin Pearce</a>.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">We love teaching <strong>complete beginners</strong> but we also teach&nbsp;<strong><a href="surfing-lessons/advanced-coaching.html">Intermediate and Advanced&nbsp;Surf Coaching</a> </strong>and are <strong>the only surf school in Taghazout offering outback, technical &amp; progressive surf lessons</strong> on a daily basis.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">We are a <strong>Specialist Surf School</strong>, in that we <strong>only teach Surfing</strong>. Our instructors are focused on their Surf Coaching, and not distracted by offering kayak lessons, coasteering, paddleboarding etc, so if you want to learn to surf or improve your surfing, with <strong>Specialist Surf Coaches</strong>&nbsp;then look no further.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">We are open <strong>12 months of the year, 7 days a week,</strong>&nbsp;closed only on Christmas Day, Boxing Day &amp; New Years Day. Whatever the time of year, you can receive the best Surf Coaching from the experienced team at Argana Surf School.</p> 



